             was indicted for <rs id="t18180909-218-off1194" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18180909-218-off1194" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180909-218-off1194" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18180909-218-cd1195" type="crimeDate">3d of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180909-218-off1194 t18180909-218-cd1195"></join>, 5lbs. of soap, value 4s., and 6lbs of pepper, value 16s.
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18180909-218-victim1667" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Ruddy
                  <interp inst="t18180909-218-victim1667" type="surname" value="Ruddy"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180909-218-victim1667" type="given" value="Thomas"></interp>
